---
layout: page.njk
title: Updates
eyebrow: News & Updates
subtitle: "Latest news from the I-PACE Owners' Advocacy Group."
description: "News and updates from the I-PACE Owners' Advocacy Group."
---

{% if collections.updates.length %}
  <div class="stack">
    {% for post in collections.updates %}
      <article class="dashboard-panel"{% if post.data.fullModeOnly %} data-site-mode-only="full"{% endif %}>
        <div class="dashboard-panel__header">
          <h2 class="dashboard-panel__title" style="font-size: var(--text-xl);">
            <a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a>
          </h2>
          <time datetime="{{ post.date | isoDate }}" style="font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-text-muted);">
            {{ post.date | readableDate }}
          </time>
        </div>
        {% if post.data.summary %}
          <p style="color: var(--color-text-muted); margin-bottom: 0;">{{ post.data.summary }}</p>
        {% endif %}
      </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
{% else %}
  <div class="callout callout--info">
    <span class="callout__icon" aria-hidden="true">📢</span>
    <div class="callout__content">
      <p class="callout__title">Updates coming soon</p>
      <p>We'll post news about the group, evidence collection milestones, and any developments here.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
{% endif %}
